{"tid":270463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 民協馮檢基：六四是一種信仰","createTime":"2017-06-04T10:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T16:55:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4138c8a8bfe39851c297aa9eb97114ffa25f8b","tid":270463,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://64.appledaily.com.hk/news/all/56782736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F64.appledaily.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fall%2F56782736&d=66fmDsL%2FhYXocGNv46SWAhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e777ebc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://64.appledaily.com.hk/news/all/56782736</a><br />\n<br />\n近年新一代不滿支聯會行禮如儀搞六四維園燭光集會，多間大學學生會已表明不出席晚會，中大七間書院學生會今午舉行聯書院六四論壇，主題為「香港中國，漸行漸遠；六四意義，從何說起」，立法會議員羅冠聰、楊岳橋、資深傳媒人謝志峰、前立法會議黃毓民均有出席。<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民批評支聯會燭光集會行禮如儀是變相維穩，「共產黨係樂見你每年有呢啲燭光」、「表面上就無嘢，內心就喜之」，因「至少你愛國，愛國就得傾」。他認為打倒共產黨才是六四悼念的宗旨，籲支聯會改口號。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">民協馮檢基回應黃毓民的維穩論指，每年六四燭光集會已漸漸變得非只是一個儀式，已是變成一種信仰，他認為只有繼續在香港傳播，才能有更多人知道這段歷史。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f041f88d4b19f698cc534a68af90c96297a26665","tid":270463,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"《香港獨立論》講過, 係叫「六四教」<br />\n<br />\n《獨立論》好勁！"},{"pid":"e4073e1762503000d44f8e0b7edebcd63df0df85","tid":270463,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《香港獨立論》講過, 係叫「六四教」<br />\n<br />\n《獨立論》好勁！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28c46f0ccadeab6ffb5dc73e8ac3830b523d475","tid":270463,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"64 教"},{"pid":"4020ebdc7555fbbcf9b5b33bd8c3ba862fe4448f","tid":270463,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0149f72e8aca725b8d248738c0d6b9821f4153b","tid":270463,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_KA/kalaok/PSN_PHOTO/004/f_17046004_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_KA%2Fkalaok%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F004%2Ff_17046004_1.jpg&h=2c5956b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06e43a4826473b8ec51e6173d00d68fd0dfdd379","tid":270463,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/18920606_10154829314338681_3462516024533896430_n.jpg?oh=c68e67b3bc590dfd2efab076b98d0e52&amp;oe=59ABC916\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F18920606_10154829314338681_3462516024533896430_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dc68e67b3bc590dfd2efab076b98d0e52%26oe%3D59ABC916&h=e1edddb9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}